<B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Century Schoolbook">Summary:</FONT></B><I><FONT SIZE=2 
FACE="Century Schoolbook"> 
</FONT></I><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Century Schoolbook">Although several 
episodes have implied approval for premarital sex, <I>First Time</I>'s 
visuals and dialogue have not been explicitly prurient. Marijuana 
use and disrespect for law enforcement have been countenanced. 
