href="/townhall/columnists/">Columnists</a> ] </center> <!a
href="/townhall/columnists/weyrich.html"><!Biography> <p> <h3> Wednesday, December 18, 1996
</h3> <h2>People Are Tired Of The Media Elite</h2> <P> <blockquote> <p> <DD>The Media
