<li>Discover how states are taking power back from the federal government in <i>Policy Review</i>'s <a href="/heritage/p_review/jan96/labs.html">"Laboratories of Democracy."</a>
<li>Gary Bauer comments on the rising instances of <a href="/townhall/FRC/radio/c95l21.html">drug abuse</a> in American teenagers.
<li>Phyllis Schlafly's newest column, <a href="/townhall/columnists/schl1220.html">"Bi-Lingualism is Wrong Way to Go."</a>  
</ul>
<b>12/20/95</b>
<ul>
